{{Infobox location |name = Atoll Ferronis Hulk |image = Atoll Ferronis Hulk.jpg |caption = Atoll Ferronis Hulk |type = [[Rest Spot (XC3)|Rest Spot]] |located = [[Erythia Sea]] ([[Baldotas Atoll]]) |inhabitants = |weather = |connects to = |music = }} '''Atoll Ferronis Hulk''' (Japanese: {{lang|ja|環礁の朽ちた鉄巨神}}, ''Kanshō no Kuchita Tetsukyoshin'') is a [[Rest Spot (XC3)|Rest Spot]] in {{XC3}}. It is located on the [[Baldotas Atoll]] in [[Erythia Sea]]. To activate this [[Ferronis Hulk]], the party must complete the [[Quest (XC3)|quest]] ''[[The Atoll Hulk]]''. {{clr}}
