{{Infobox XC3 Status |title = Attack Down |caption = Reduces damage dealt. |image = XC3 Attack Down.png |type = Debuff |attribute = Physical |base-duration = 15.0s |max-duration = 30.0s |success-rate = 75% |rng-applicable = Yes |effect-title-1 = Base Attack Decrease |effect-value-1 = 25% }} '''Attack Down''' is a [[Status Effect]] in {{XC3}} and {{XC3FR|sublink}}. It decreases enemy or player attack when it is cast. A separate debuff known as [[Flame Clock#Gameplay|Flame Clock Low, Attack Down]] exists during the first chapter when the party is still under the control of the Flame Clock.
